beer.beer_description:
Imperial Stout with coffee and chocolate.

Brewed for Xmas Day, but let's be honest - any day is stout day!

Perhaps we're bucking the trend for a summer release, but there really is no bad time to enjoy a rich, roasty imperial stout.

This tasty number has been subtly flavoured with espresso and chocolate, for an anytime treat.

Share with good friends.
